columns.name: date_of_death
columns.formula:
dob = date_of_birth || now()
birth_year = year(dob)
curr_year = year(now())
life_span = curr_year - birth_year
death_year = dob + years(random(1, life_span))

if is_deceased == true && !date_of_birth.nil?
  death_year
else
  nil
end
